snippet.title: Buzz! The Big Quiz PS2 Multiplayer Gameplay (SCEE) Playstation 2
snippet.description:
In this video me and Wiggy G battle it out on Buzz! the big quiz, for the Sony Playstation 2. Not really a lot to say about this one. The second installment in the buzz collection, this one is based more on general knowledge. 
Wiggy G takes the crown in this video, it was close at times but my knowledge seems to be anything but general lol. 

Check out my other videos, and please leave a comment or like
